<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/wordle/favicon.svg">
	<title>404 - Page non trouvée</title>
	<style>
		body {
			background-color: #121213;
			color: #ffffff;
			font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
			justify-content: center;
			min-height: 100vh;
			margin: 0;
			padding: 2rem;
			overflow: hidden;
		}

		.error-container {
			text-align: center;
			max-width: 600px;
			animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out;
		}

		@keyframes fadeInUp {
			from {
				opacity: 0;
				transform: translateY(30px);
			}
			to {
				opacity: 1;
				transform: translateY(0);
			}
		}

		.error-code {
			font-size: 8rem;
			font-weight: bold;
			color: #538d4e;
			margin: 0;
			text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(83, 141, 78, 0.3);
			animation: pulse 2s infinite ease-in-out;
		}

		@keyframes pulse {
			0%, 100% {
				transform: scale(1);
				text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(83, 141, 78, 0.3);
			}
			50% {
				transform: scale(1.05);
				text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(83, 141, 78, 0.5);
			}
		}

		.error-title {
			font-size: 2rem;
			margin: 1rem 0;
			color: #ffffff;
		}

		.error-message {
			font-size: 1.2rem;
			color: #8e9297;
			margin: 2rem 0;
			line-height: 1.6;
		}

		.wordle-tiles {
			display: flex;
			justify-content: center;
			gap: 0.5rem;
			margin: 2rem 0;
		}

		.tile {
			width: 3rem;
			height: 3rem;
			border: 2px solid #3a3a3c;
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
			justify-content: center;
			font-size: 1.5rem;
			font-weight: bold;
			text-transform: uppercase;
			border-radius: 4px;
			animation: tileFlip 0.6s ease-in-out forwards;
		}

		.tile:nth-child(1) {
			animation-delay: 0.1s;
			background-color: #b59f3b;
			border-color: #b59f3b;
		}

		.tile:nth-child(2) {
			animation-delay: 0.3s;
			background-color: #3a3a3c;
			border-color: #3a3a3c;
		}

		.tile:nth-child(3) {
			animation-delay: 0.5s;
			background-color: #3a3a3c;
			border-color: #3a3a3c;
		}

		.tile:nth-child(4) {
			animation-delay: 0.7s;
			background-color: #538d4e;
			border-color: #538d4e;
		}

		.tile:nth-child(5) {
			animation-delay: 0.9s;
			background-color: #3a3a3c;
			border-color: #3a3a3c;
		}

		@keyframes tileFlip {
			0% {
				transform: rotateX(0);
				background-color: transparent;
				border-color: #3a3a3c;
			}
			50% {
				transform: rotateX(90deg);
			}
			100% {
				transform: rotateX(0);
			}
		}

		.home-link {
			color: #ffffff;
			text-decoration: none;
			font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
			font-size: 1rem;
			cursor: pointer;
			transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
		}

		.home-link:hover {
			opacity: 0.7;
			text-decoration: underline;
		}

		.floating-letters {
			position: absolute;
			top: 0;
			left: 0;
			width: 100%;
			height: 100%;
			pointer-events: none;
			overflow: hidden;
			z-index: -1;
		}

		.floating-letter {
			position: absolute;
			color: rgba(83, 141, 78, 0.1);
			font-size: 2rem;
			font-weight: bold;
			animation: float 10s infinite linear;
		}

		@keyframes float {
			0% {
				transform: translateY(100vh) rotate(0deg);
				opacity: 0;
			}
			10% {
				opacity: 1;
			}
			90% {
				opacity: 1;
			}
			100% {
				transform: translateY(-100px) rotate(360deg);
				opacity: 0;
			}
		}

		.suggestion {
			background-color: #1a1a1b;
			border: 2px solid #3a3a3c;
			border-radius: 8px;
			padding: 1.5rem;
			margin: 2rem 0;
			color: #d7dadc;
		}

		.suggestion h3 {
			color: #ffffff;
			margin-bottom: 1rem;
			font-size: 1.3rem;
		}

		.suggestion ul {
			list-style: none;
			padding: 0;
			margin: 0;
		}

		.suggestion li {
			padding: 0.5rem 0;
			border-bottom: 1px solid #3a3a3c;
		}

		.suggestion li:last-child {
			border-bottom: none;
		}

		.suggestion a {
			color: #538d4e;
			text-decoration: none;
			transition: color 0.2s;
		}

		.suggestion a:hover {
			color: #5fa35a;
			text-decoration: underline;
		}

		@media (max-width: 768px) {
			.error-code {
				font-size: 6rem;
			}

			.error-title {
				font-size: 1.5rem;
			}

			.error-message {
				font-size: 1rem;
			}

			.tile {
				width: 2.5rem;
				height: 2.5rem;
				font-size: 1.2rem;
			}
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="floating-letters">
		<span class="floating-letter" style="left: 10%; animation-delay: 0s;">W</span>
		<span class="floating-letter" style="left: 20%; animation-delay: 2s;">O</span>
		<span class="floating-letter" style="left: 30%; animation-delay: 4s;">R</span>
		<span class="floating-letter" style="left: 40%; animation-delay: 6s;">D</span>
		<span class="floating-letter" style="left: 50%; animation-delay: 8s;">L</span>
		<span class="floating-letter" style="left: 60%; animation-delay: 1s;">E</span>
		<span class="floating-letter" style="left: 70%; animation-delay: 3s;">4</span>
		<span class="floating-letter" style="left: 80%; animation-delay: 5s;">2</span>
		<span class="floating-letter" style="left: 90%; animation-delay: 7s;">!</span>
	</div>
	<div class="error-container">
		<h1 class="error-code">404</h1>
		<h2 class="error-title">Oops! Page non trouvée</h2>
		<div class="wordle-tiles">
			<div class="tile">E</div>
			<div class="tile">R</div>
			<div class="tile">R</div>
			<div class="tile">O</div>
			<div class="tile">R</div>
		</div>
		<p class="error-message">
			Désolé, la page que vous recherchez semble avoir disparu dans les méandres du web.
			Peut-être avez-vous fait une faute de frappe, ou peut-être que cette page n'existe tout simplement pas.
		</p>
		<div class="home-button">
			<a href="/" class="home-link">← Retour à l'accueil</a>
		</div>
	</div>
	<script>
		document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
			const tiles = document.querySelectorAll('.tile');
			tiles.forEach((tile, index) => {
				setTimeout(() => {
					tile.style.animationPlayState = 'running';
				}, index * 200);
			});
		});
		document.querySelector('.error-code').addEventListener('click', function() {
			this.style.animation = 'pulse 0.3s ease-in-out';
			setTimeout(() => {
				this.style.animation = 'pulse 2s infinite ease-in-out';
			}, 300);
		});
	</script>
</body>
</html>
